message.content: cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.AI, cs.ET - The paper discusses the teaching of formal methods in engineering, which is closely related to the field of logic (cs.LO). The application of logic in engineering also has connections to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and emerging technologies (cs.ET).
